l, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "GC_SHROOMLAGOON_2560x1440.png", "id": "147535778279727", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974843_147535781613060_909788482911663441_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=txfWrIcY3OUQ7kNvgFGzFMy&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAAeQFWTKKDMJpLmP5pp55YmpHBQ5U0CvRKF4rHmvJd7A&oe=676D36B3"}, "display_name": "Galactic Catch", "keywords": ["fishing", "simulator", "fish", "baobab", "sports"], "long_description": "Great for all ages! Play the latest out-of-this-world fishing game from Baobab Studios, 9x Emmy-winning creators of the fan-favorite, \"Invasion!\" \n\nFEATURES:\n\ud83c\udf0b Explore strange and wild new worlds\n\ud83d\udc1f Catch 60+ types of cosmic fish \n\ud83c\udfa3 Customize and power up your rods and reels\n\ud83e\udeb8 Craft your aquarium with decor and prized fish \n\ud83c\udfb6 Escape reality with relaxing melodies \n\ud83d\udc33 Save your friends Mac & Cheez (if you can!)\n\nHave a fin-tastic time as you go fishing across galaxies. Take on the role of a trusted robot on a mission to save your friends Mac & Cheez. Catch wonderous alien fish across strange worlds, craft and power up your fishing gear, go on challenging missions, and customize your aquarium with unique decor and prized fish.\n\nJoin our official Discord for more fun and expansive lore outside the game! \n", "short_description": "Play the latest galactic fishing game from Baobab Studios,  Emmy-winning creators of fan-favorite, \"Invasion!\" \n\nHave a fin-tastic time as you fish across galaxies. Take on the role of a trusted robot on a mission to save your friends.\n\nFEATURES:\n\ud83c\udf0b Explore strange and wild new worlds\n\ud83d\udc1f Catch 60+ types of cosmic fish \n\ud83c\udfa3 Customize and power up your rods and reels\n\ud83e\udeb8 Craft your aquarium with decor and prized fish \n\ud83c\udfb6 Escape reality with relaxing melodies \n\ud83d\udc33 Save your friends Mac & Cheez "}]}